# Step 4: Set Up GitHub

## Creating a GitHub Account

1. Follow the instructions on <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1cE-x93hhE1xLfxy8qnJlkwe1-hSyKhpO01Uo03aqnhU/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">**Getting Started on GitHub**</a> to create your GitHub account.

2. Then follow the instructions on <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZeT9iXkmxAxTbtmFWfrLMsFneicKOzvx4cYogntwfOE/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">**GitHub Student Developer Pack**</a> to obtain verified student access on GitHub.

